<article class="post post-page content-item page">
    <header>
        

<h1>Welcome!</h1>
    </header>
    <p>Beautifully situated campsites in an old growth forest connecting to the 'off leash' Mouat Park Trails, just a 10-minute walk to all the amenities in downtown Ganges. All the walk-in tent sites and the camper/RV sites have fire rings. The water throughout the campground is good for drinking and there are water and electric hook-ups in the camper/RV sites. We are well supervised, and we welcome both children and camping friendly dogs.</p>
<p>Miss our previous website? Find it <a href="http://buddha.cloudapp.net/PreviousWebsite/index.html">here</a>. </p>
    </article>
</div>
                </div>
                            <div>
