<ul>
<li>Rates inc. one tent or one RV and two adults.</li>
<li>Serviced R.V. rates inc. 15 amp power and water.</li>
<li>Extra people are $8 per night.</li>
<li>Children under 14 are free.</li>
<li>WIFI is included.</li>
<li>Three day reservations are required for long weekends for drive in sites.</li>
</ul>
