<article class="widget-after-content widget-html-widget widget">
    <header id="mouat-park-trail">
        <h1>Mouat Park Trail</h1>        
                
    </header>
    <p>Enjoy a beautiful walk to town, through the Mouat Park trails, which connect directly to our campground.</p>
<p>For information on all of our Parks and Trail maps go to <a href="http://www.crd.bc.ca/ssiparc" target="_blank">www.crd.bc.ca/ssiparc/</a>.</p>
<p>And we are just a block away from the fairgrounds, where the annual, 100+ year old <a href="http://ssifi.org/fall-fair">Fall Fair</a> is held each September.</p>
<p><img alt="" src="/Media/Default/OtherImages/mouat_park_trails_600x400.png" height="400" width="600" /></p>
</article>
