<article class="widget-after-content widget-html-widget widget">
    <header id="links">
        <h1>Links</h1>        
                
    </header>
    <p>...to transportation, things to do and see while on Salt Spring Island.</p>
<p><a href="http://hellosaltspring.com/">Hello, Salt Spring</a> details activities to do on the island.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.toursaltspring.com">Western Splendour Tour Company</a> is a tour company located on Salt Spring Island.</p>
<p><a href="http://gulfislandsdriftwood.com/">Gulf Islands Driftwood</a> weekly newspaper. Coverage of local news as well as 7 day events calendar.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.saltspringtoday.com/">Salt Spring Island Chamber of Commerce</a> - Discover an island paradise... Salt Spring Island, BC.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.crd.bc.ca/ssiparc/activity/rainbowroad/index.htm">Rainbow Road Indoor Pool</a> - Admission fees, opening times and special programs - Phone 250-537-1402.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.bcferries.com/schedules/">BC Ferries Schedule</a> - Look up Salt Spring Island and choose your point of arrival: Vesuvius, Fulford or Long Harbour.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.saltspringair.com">Salt Spring Air</a>, <a href="http://www.harbour-air.com">HarbourAir</a> and <a href="http://www.seairseaplanes.com">SeaAir</a>: If you choose to fly in, there are three airlines offering float plane service to the island.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.bctransit.com/regions/ssi/schedules/">Bus Service</a> - operates between ferry terminals and Ganges, and around the village of Ganges... with a bike carrier.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.lorenda.ca/">L'Orenda Sailing Charters</a> - Cruise the beautiful Gulf Islands onboard a classic North Sea gaff-rigged yawl.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.islandescapades.com/">Island Escapades</a> - Eco-adventures in the Gulf Islands since 1991. Two hour to full day kayak.</p>
<p><a href="HTTP://www.crd.bc.ca/ssiparc/.">Parks and Trail Maps</a>&nbsp;- Information on all of our Parks and Trail maps.</p>
<p><a href="http://ssifi.org/fall-fair">Fall Fair</a>&nbsp;-&nbsp;100+ year old Fall Fair is held each September.</p>
</article></div>
